OL,3,CHomelessness in England rises by more
OL,4,Cthan 12% in past year
OL,6,FHomelessness in England has increased
OL,7,Fby more than 12 per cent in the past
OL,8,Fyear, according to official statistics.
OL,10,FIn the year leading up to March 2024,
OL,11,F178,560 households were assessed as
OL,12,Fhomeless.
OL,14,FIt marks a 12.3 per cent increase on
OL,15,Fthe previous financial year, according
OL,16,Fto the government report on statutory
OL,17,Fhomelessness.
