OL,3,CHomelessness in England rises by more
OL,4,Cthan 12% in past year
OL,6,FMeanwhile, 146,430 households were at
OL,7,Fthreat of homelessness in the same
OL,8,Fperiod which represents a 3.1 per cent
OL,9,Frise on the previous year.
OL,11,FThese increases have been experienced
OL,12,Fboth by households with or without
OL,13,Fchildren.
OL,15,FPolly Neate, chief executive of
OL,16,Fhomelessness charity Shelter, has
OL,17,Fcalled on the government to offer more
OL,18,Fsupport.
