OL,6,FShe said: "No child should have to
OL,7,Fface the trauma of growing up
OL,8,Fhomeless. The housing emergency has
OL,9,Ftrapped many families in temporary
OL,10,Faccommodation for over five years.
OL,12,F"Overpriced private rentals and the
OL,13,Flack of genuinely affordable social
OL,14,Fhomes are pushing families into
OL,15,Fhomelessness and insecure temporary
OL,16,Faccommodation.
