OL,3,CHomelessness in England rises by more
OL,4,Cthan 12% in past year
OL,6,F"Families are crammed into small
OL,7,Frooms, sharing kitchens and bathrooms
OL,8,Fwith strangers and living out of
OL,9,Fsuitcases, worrying they could be
OL,10,Fmoved miles away overnight.
OL,12,F"The government must act to end
OL,13,Fhomelessness for good.
OL,15,FTo help families out of damaging
OL,16,Ftemporary accommodation into a settled
OL,17,Fhome the government must set a target
OL,18,Fand invest in building genuinely
OL,19,Faffordable social homes.
OL,21,F"We need 90,000 a year for ten years."
