OL,3,CHomelessness in England rises by more
OL,4,Cthan 12% in past year
OL,6,FOverall, 324,990 households were found
OL,7,Fto either be homeless or on the brink
OL,8,Fof it.
OL,10,FThe number of households with children
OL,11,Fthat were either at risk of
OL,12,Fhomelessness or already homeless rose
OL,13,Fby 3.9 per cent.
OL,15,FIn addition, households with children
OL,16,Fin temporary accommodation increased
OL,17,Fby 14.7 per cent to 74,530.
