OL,3,CHomelessness in England rises by more
OL,4,Cthan 12% in past year
OL,6,FRushanara Ali, Minister for
OL,7,FHomelessness, said: "These numbers are
OL,8,Fmore than just statistics.
OL,10,F"They show the devastating impact
OL,11,Fhomelessness has on peoples' lives and
OL,12,Fit is shocking that so many, including
OL,13,Ffamilies with children, are spending
OL,14,Fyears without a place to call home.
OL,16,F"We are taking action to tackle the
OL,17,Froot causes of homelessness ` not just
OL,18,Fits symptoms ` putting in place
OL,19,Flasting solutions rather than quick
OL,20,Ffixes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
