OL,3,CHomelessness in England rises by more
OL,4,Cthan 12% in past year
OL,6,F"We are reversing the worst housing
OL,7,Fcrisis in living history by building
OL,8,F1.5 million new homes and are changing
OL,9,Fthe law to abolish Section 21 'no
OL,10,Ffault' evictions ` immediately
OL,11,Ftackling one of the leading causes of
OL,12,Fhomelessness.
OL,14,F"In addition, we've announced a new
OL,15,Fdedicated cross government group,
OL,16,Ftasked with creating a long-term
OL,17,Fstrategy to end the disgraceful levels
OL,18,Fof homelessness."
